target_col = "Solar8000/NIBP_SBP"

case_ratios = []
for cid in case_ids:
    df_case = signals.get(cid, None)
    if df_case is None or not isinstance(df_case, pd.DataFrame):
        continue
    if target_col not in df_case.columns:
        continue

    s = df_case[target_col].dropna()
    if s.shape[0] == 0:
        continue

    case_ratios.append((s >= 140).mean())

result = float(np.mean(case_ratios)) if len(case_ratios) > 0 else float("nan")
